/www.uradni-list.si/dl/vip_akti/1990-02-2102.pdf |dead-url=no }}{{cite news |url=http://www.reporter.si/node/692 |title=Intervju: Rosvita Pesek |language=sl |trans_title=Interview: Rosvita Pesek |date=2008-12-26 |newspaper=Reporter |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606033211/http://www.reporter.si/node/692 |archivedate=2012-06-06 |accessdate=2015-12-24 }}</ref><ref name="Delo">{{cite web |url=http://www.delo.si/novice/politika/plebiscit-o-samostojnosti-cas-najvecje-politicne-enotnosti.html |title=Plebiscit o samostojnosti - čas največje politične enotnosti |language=sl |trans_title=Independence Referendum - the Time of the Largest Political Unity |publisher=Delo.si |date=2011-11-23 |issn=1854-6544 |accessdate=2015-12-24 |archive-date=2020-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830223738/https://www.delo.si/novice/politika/plebiscit-o-samostojnosti-cas-najvecje-politicne-enotnosti.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。投票結果顯示總選民的88.5%（投票者的94.8%）支持斯洛維尼亞獨立<ref name="Juberias">{{cite book |url=http://crnvo.me/docs/biblio_eng/p10.pdf |title=Legal Aspects for Referendum in Montenegro in the Context of International Law and Practice |date=November 2005 |chapter=Some legal (and political) considerations about the legal framework for referendum in Montenegro, in the light of European experiences and standards |last=Flores Juberías |first=Carlos |page=74 |publisher=Foundation Open Society Institute, Representative Office Montenegro |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426081759/http://crnvo.me/docs/biblio_eng/p10.pdf |archivedate=2012-04-26 |access-date=2015-12-24 }}</ref>。

